Subject: [PATCH 76/99] FROMLIST(v6): arm64: dts: amlogic: Add Amlogic S4 Audio

Add basic audio driver support for the Amlogic S4 based
Amlogic AQ222 board.

Signed-off-by: Jiebing Chen <jiebing.chen@amlogic.com>
---
 .../dts/amlogic/meson-s4-s805x2-aq222.dts     | 222 +++++++++++
